org.eclipse.scada.vi.model

Interface Symbol

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SymbolImpl

    public interface Symbol
    A representation of the model object 'Symbol'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Root
    • Properties
    • On Init
    • On Dispose
    • On Update
    • Script Modules
    • Cursors
    • Background Color
    • Design Size
    • Connections

    See Also:
    VisualInterfacePackage.getSymbol()
